- Scrollbars handle visibility when computing max value
- Window's ScrollBar visibility status are auto-inclusive
- LocalTest works again (was broken since several months)
- Fix a bug in wdmulticolumnlist::drawOneHeader scissor bottom
- Fix a bug in wdmulticolumnlist::drawAllItems scissor bottom
- Adds an indentation to the MultiColumnList's header caption
- Fix the MultiColumnList border column bug
- QuadRenerer::debug SEGFAULT fixed
- Window's resize attraction bug fixed
- Window::computeMinimumSize() implementation
- All files individually docommented
